name: Kendrick Lamar
summary: In the wake of his ongoing feud with Drake, Kendrick Lamar has released a music video for his latest single, "Not Like Us." The video, which is a celebratory ode to the West Coast, has been met with widespread praise for its stunning visuals and Lamar's scathing lyrics directed at his rival. The video sees Lamar taking victory laps, mocking Drake's "Hotline Bling" dance moves, and even taming an owl, in a symbolic display of his dominance. The release of the video has further escalated the feud between the two rappers, with Lamar taking direct aim at Drake in several of the song's lyrics. The video has also sparked a debate about the use of artificial intelligence in music, as it features a prominent AI-generated backing track.
